<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-07-23T04:25:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-07-23T04:25:00-05:00" n="661" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d661">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">765.84/604: Telegram</note>
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Ethiopia</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">George</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                            State</gloss>
                                    </hi>
                                </head>
                                <opener>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                                        <placeName>
                                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Addis Ababa</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-07-23T12:00:00+02:35">July 23, 1935—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received July 23—8:50
                                        a.m.]</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p>61. Italian Minister, protesting Emperor’s latest speech,
                                    declined to attend official reception or dinner Emperor’s
                                    birthday today. Rupture of diplomatic relations may result. I
                                    was most graciously received at impressive ceremonies this
                                    morning at Palace and returning therefrom loudly acclaimed all
                                    along route by cries of Live America.</p>
                                <closer>
                                    <signed>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">George</hi>
                                    </signed>
                                </closer>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>